The paper introduces a novel approach for detecting anomalies in radio signals using recurrent neural networks. This involves processing complex multi-user radio bands, which suggests that the paper could fall under the categories of neural networks (cs.NE), information theory (cs.IT), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and systems and control (cs.SY).
